{"title":"诗三首","authors":["胡耀邦"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡耀邦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜月皎皎到中庭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弱女浓妆理素琴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗前嘎然一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"料是孤鸿落寒汀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世事匆匆各浮沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风云叱咤多女英。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死神面前犹奋笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君是巾帼罕见人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沧桑变化寻常事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间悲欢最牵魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能偷得蟠桃果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怜取卿卿锦绣文。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九八七年九月二十五日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}